    {
        "content": "<p>So, we just merged a major change in how emoji in messages are handled.  It also includes a smaller change in how emoji reactions are handled (fixing flag emoji, etc.).</p>",
        "id": 289862,
        "sender_full_name": "Tim Abbott",
        "timestamp": 1506709294
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Finally! <span class=\"emoji emoji-1f60c\" title=\"relieved\">:relieved:</span></p>",
